HEADWORD: geta
<hw>get"a</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Jap.]</ety> <def>A type of Japanese
footwear usually with wooden soles, held to the foot by a thong that
passes between the first two toes.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> clog, patten, sabot.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

